Powersave

/etc/fstab - prefer relatime over atime.
cpufreq-info - list CPU frequency settings and capabilities.
cpufreq-set - change CPU frequency settings. Examples: -g ondemand|performance|powersave. Recommended: ondemand.
modprobe p4-clockmod - does NOT save power, only prevents overheating.
desktop effects (compositing) do not use more power. (Good power management practices)
